and never come back?

364
00:37:28,360 --> 00:37:33,036
First, they want to see you.
Make sure you've got the real goods.

365
00:37:33,200 --> 00:37:35,077
Then your ass is theirs.

366
00:37:35,240 --> 00:37:38,038
Then they take your car
and stick a bomb in it.

367
00:37:38,200 --> 00:37:40,839
