368
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:44,072
But you're not.
You're on vacation at Club Fed.

369
00:37:44,240 --> 00:37:47,118
When they say they want to
talk to you, are they lying?

370
00:37:47,280 --> 00:37:50,033
Of course they're lying.

371
00:37:50,200 --> 00:37:54,034
If you can read minds,
why don't you know that?

372
00:37:57,360 --> 00:38:00,432
She's quite the smart-ass.

373
00:38:02,000 --> 00:38:04,150
My girl.

374
00:38:13,560 --> 00:38:17,678
- Gordon's not getting any tonight.
- She's pissed.

375
00:38:17,840 --> 00:38:19,910
Go get her, cowboy.

376
00:38:26,160 --> 00:38:28,993
- Are you all right?
- No, I'm not.

377
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:33,076
- We were just kidding around.
- Don't you get it?

378
00:38:33,240 --> 00:38:37,279
They'll tell you a joke one minute,
the next, they'll shoot you in the head.

379
00:38:37,440 --> 00:38:40,398
They're not waving guns at us any more.

380
00:38:40,560 --> 00:38:43,632
