they don't kill us.

381
00:38:44,120 --> 00:38:46,076
Gordon?

382
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:49,471
Is it possible
that you admire these people?

383
00:38:49,640 --> 00:38:51,517
Not admire...

384
00:38:52,320 --> 00:38:55,869
They're going to make more this week
than I'll make all year.

385
00:38:56,040 --> 00:38:57,951
I can't believe you're saying this.

386
00:38:58,120 --> 00:39:02,875
A week ago, you wouldn't have had
anything to do with people like this.

387
00:39:03,640 --> 00:39:07,189
- I know what I'm doing.
- You don't have a clue.

388
00:39:07,360 --> 00:39:10,830
That's enough!
Let's go back and join the others.

389
00:39:16,320 --> 00:39:18,914
I'll be back in a minute.

390
00:39:28,520 --> 00:39:31,751
- I'm going to bed.
- Me too.

391
00:39:32,160 --> 00:39:35,994
- Good night, Ray.
- Sweet dreams.

392
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:43,393
I'm going to get another beer.
Marcus, you want a beer?

393
00:39:44,240 --> 00:39:45,878
Yeah, just get me one.

394
00:39:46,040 --> 00:39:48,600
- Gordo?
- Fine.

395
00:39:59,160 --> 00:40:02,709
What the fuck are you doing?
You think this is cool?

396
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:04,233
No.

397
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:08,029
- Why are you kissing everybody's ass?
